title: Maria Kanellis
summary: Mary Louis Kanellis-Bennett[7][8][9] (born February 25, 1982)[1] is an American professional wrestler, professional wrestling manager, actress, model and singer who is best known for her time with Ring of Honor (ROH).[10] She is also best known for her time in WWE. She is also known for her 2008 Playboy magazine pictorial and 2010 appearances on the Celebrity Apprentice television series.
